name: Outside Inside Freestyle Battle Disk
description: Packable and portable pole-perched poultry pelting. This fun game tests your disc-throwing accuracy on camping trips or in the backyard.Telescopic poles complete with water-fillable bases.Includes flying disc and 2 chicken targets.Includes mesh carrying bag and set-up instructions.Set-up dimensions are 112 x 30cm. Chickens are 20cm tall. Disk is 28cm in diameter.
